Note:
Runa Standard Library: AI Context Situation Module Stub

This stub file contains all type definitions and function signatures for the
AI situation assessment system, enabling compiler semantic analysis and type checking.

The situation assessment system provides comprehensive situation awareness,
threat assessment, opportunity recognition, dynamic situation modeling, and real-time situation tracking.
:End Note

Note: Core Type Definitions
Type SituationAssessmentSystem is Dictionary with:
    system_id as String
    assessment_paradigm as String
    situation_sensors as List[SituationSensor]
    situation_analyzers as List[SituationAnalyzer]
    threat_assessors as List[ThreatAssessor]
    opportunity_detectors as List[OpportunityDetector]
    situation_models as List[SituationModel]
    decision_support as DecisionSupport
    system_configuration as SystemConfiguration

Type SituationSensor is Dictionary with:
    sensor_id as String
    sensor_type as String
    sensing_capabilities as List[SensingCapability]
    data_sources as List[DataSource]
    sensor_fusion as SensorFusion
    sensor_reliability as Float
    sensor_coverage as SensorCoverage
    sensor_configuration as SensorConfiguration

Type SituationAnalyzer is Dictionary with:
    analyzer_id as String
    analysis_type as String
    analysis_algorithms as List[AnalysisAlgorithm]
    situation_classifiers as List[SituationClassifier]
    context_interpreters as List[ContextInterpreter]
    uncertainty_handlers as List[UncertaintyHandler]
    analyzer_performance as AnalyzerPerformance

Type ThreatAssessor is Dictionary with:
    assessor_id as String
    threat_categories as List[String]
    threat_detection as ThreatDetection
    risk_assessment as RiskAssessment
    threat_modeling as ThreatModeling
    mitigation_strategies as List[MitigationStrategy]
    threat_prioritization as ThreatPrioritization
    assessor_configuration as AssessorConfiguration

Type OpportunityDetector is Dictionary with:
    detector_id as String
    opportunity_types as List[String]
    detection_algorithms as List[DetectionAlgorithm]
    opportunity_evaluation as OpportunityEvaluation
    feasibility_assessment as FeasibilityAssessment
    opportunity_ranking as OpportunityRanking
    detector_performance as DetectorPerformance

Type SituationModel is Dictionary with:
    model_id as String
    model_type as String
    model_components as List[ModelComponent]
    situation_variables as List[SituationVariable]
    relationship_models as List[RelationshipModel]
    state_representations as List[StateRepresentation]
    model_validation as ModelValidation
    model_evolution as ModelEvolution

Type SituationState is Dictionary with:
    state_id as String
    state_timestamp as Integer
    situation_type as String
    state_variables as Dictionary[String, Any]
    state_confidence as Float
    state_stability as Float
    threat_level as String
    opportunity_level as String
    state_duration as Float

Type Situation is Dictionary with:
    situation_id as String
    situation_name as String
    situation_type as String
    situation_category as String
    situation_description as String
    situation_context as SituationContext
    situation_participants as List[SituationParticipant]
    situation_timeline as SituationTimeline
    situation_outcomes as List[SituationOutcome]
